node.text:
Currently bawling my eyes out because I’ve been waiting over a year for this day to come! 😭🙏
.
I poured SO much love, sweat, tears (& waffle mix 😉) into this cookbook & I am so very proud of what I created.
.
This is more than just a cookbook, though. On top of the 90 delicious, macro-friendly recipes, I also included my fit tips & quick & effective workouts that you can do from anywhere! Including your kitchen, or even your van if you’re like me! 🏠
.
Each recipe uses one simple, compact & not to mention cute, Dash mini waffle maker! If you’ve been here for awhile, you know how much I LOVE this thing!
.
My passion is to help as many people as possible create healthier relationships with food & fitness.
.
That’s why I created a cookbook filled with a wide variety of healthy, easy to make recipes full of amazing flavor, but not all the extra calories.
.
I used to believe that performing & looking my best, meant that I had to eat the same, boring basic foods over & over again. 
.
Then I found out the Dash mini waffle maker, & I discovered that cooking can actually be fun & that it is possible to LOVE food & LOVE my body at the same time! 💛
.
Don’t worry, I also included some treat meals. 😋
.
Recipes are also conveniently portioned to 1 or 2 servings, so it’s great for college students living in a dorm, or frequent travelers/van lifers, like me! It’s perfect for parents because it’s fun for the kids, as well as busy bees because the mini waffle maker heats in just seconds & cooks most of the recipes in this book in just a few minutes! 🙌
.
Get my Waffly Fit Cookbook AND the @bydash mini waffle maker together in a perfectly packaged gift set for JUST $24.99! 😀
.
You can also buy my book by itself for $19.99 🙌
.
Watch the full video for more info & to see the book in action! And visit my website (clairepthomas.com). Click the link in my bio to purchase directly. 🙌
.
Love you all a waffle lot! Thank you so much for your support. 💛🧇 
.
Video edit by @turningtreeproductions
.
#teamcpt #cookbook #healthyfood #healthycooking #waffles #healthywaffles #proteinwaffles #iam1stphorm #fitfood #fitfoodie #health-coac

node.text:
Back & biceps babyyyy!! 💪🔥
.
Woof this one was fire!! I had some fun with the cable machine & tried a couple new exercise variations to mix things up!
.
If you enjoy supersets, you’ll love my CPT Fit Guide 2.0. The whole 8 week training program revolves around supersets. 🙌
.
A superset is when you alternate between two exercises for one combined set with minimal rest in between. I honestly get a little bored lifting if I don’t do my exercises in a superset or in a circuit. 😅 Not only that, but supersets make your workouts faster & feel more intense! 👊
.
I’m currently alternating between bodybuilding style workouts like this one, CrossFit & bodyweight workouts.
.
If you’re interested in following a training program for any or all of these training styles, I’ve got you covered! Check out the Fit Guides I offer & personally use myself at clairepthomas.com or click the link in my bio. 💪
.
WORKOUT DEETS:
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ LYING CABLE CURLS
💥 10 reps
2️⃣ SEATED CABLE ROWS
💥 10 reps
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ DB CROSS BODY HAMMER CURLS
💥 10 reps each arm
2️⃣ NARROW GRIP PULL DOWN
💥10 reps
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ DB CURL 21’S
💥 7 low, 7 high, 7 full
2️⃣ STRAIGHT ARM STANDING HIGH ROW + STRAIGHT ARM PULL DOWN
💥 5 reps each way, each arm
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ CHIN UPS
💥 8-10 reps
2️⃣ PULL UPS
💥 8-10 reps
.
Happy Monday Fam! 💛
.
Tag your workout partner in crime who needs to get after this one & save it for your next back & biceps workout. 💪
.
.
.
#teamcpt #backworkout #backattack #backday #backandbiceps #pullups #iam1stphorm #workoutmotivation #mauihawaii #wedothework #personaltrainer #fitnesscoach

node.text:
It’s another crazy core workout challenge + GIVEAWAY! 👊🔥
.
Happy Sunday Homies! ☺️
.
Every weekend I’ll be sharing a weekly core challenge & one lucky person who tries it will receive a free CPT Fit Guide of choice!
.
D E E T S 👇
.
Complete 2-3 rounds of the following exercises:
.
1️⃣ PLATE LEG RAISES
🔥 8 reps
.
2️⃣ PLATE KNEE RAISE HOLD + KNEE RAISE HOLD
🔥 Hold until failure, drop weight
& hold until failure without weight
.
3️⃣ PLATE SIT UPS
🔥 12 reps
.
4️⃣ PLATE RUSSIAN TWISTS
🔥 12 reps each side
.
5️⃣ PLATE STANDING SIDE DIPS
🔥 12 reps each side
.
To enter the giveaway, all you have to do is film yourself or a friend attempting an exercise from this workout, tag me on your story & use the hashtag, #clairecorechallenge 💪
.
I’m NOT choosing the winners based on how well or how many reps. The weekly winner will be selected completely randomly from the pool of people who tag me throughout each week! 🙌
.
So, grab a weight plate & give this workout a shot! Tag someone who also needs to try for a chance to win one of my training programs. 💪
.
To learn more about all the programs I offer, click the link in my bio for my website!
.
I will announce the winner on my story next weekend, when I share next week’s new core challenge!
.
GOOD LUCK! 💪
.
.
.
#teamcpt #corechallenge #abs #absworkout #sixpack #sixpackabs #6packabs #corechallenge #fitnesschallenge #giveaway #strongcore #workoutmotivation #iam1stphorm #mauihawaii

node.text:
Are you a sunrise or a sunset person?
.
We’re both. ☀️
.
Haleakala (which translates to “House of Sun”) is easily one of the most breathtaking & indescribably beautiful places I’ve ever witnessed.
.
I mean, it’s a giant volcano in the middle of the ocean that created 75% of the island of Maui.
.
It has one of the world’s largest craters that quite literally looks & feels like Mars (or what I imagine Mars to be like). It’s absolutely out of this world, & you’ve gotta add it to your bucket list! 🌋
.
Where’s your favorite place to watch the sun go down or rise up?
.
.
.
#haleakala #haleakalasunrise #haleakalanationalpark #sunsetlovers #sunrise #mauihawaii #mauilife #hilife #hawaiistagram #chasingsunsets #vanlife #vanlifediaries #vanlifemovement #sprintervan

How fast can you do this fire full body workout?! 💪🔥
.
This right here is my favorite style of training. 🙌 High intensity, fast paced, athletic, don’t stop ‘til ya drop workouts are my jam! What I love most about this one is that it’s equally as mental as it is physical. How much pain and discomfort can you sustain? How hard can you really push yourself? How badly do you want it?!
.
It’s you vs. you.
.
D E E T S :
.
Complete 3 rounds of the following 4 exercises as fast as you possibly can!👇
.
💥 10 POWER CLEANS (105lbs RX women/155 men)
💥 450m ROW
💥 10 PUSH JERKS (105lbs RX women/155 men)
💥 400m RUN
.
My time was 15:41 😵
.
GET AFTER IT! 👊
.
Tag your workout buddies who would destroy this workout! 👊
.
.
.
#teamcpt #fullbodyworkout #wodoftheday #functionaltraining #functionalfitness #mauihawaii #personaltrainer #workoutmotivation

node.text:
Grab a buddy & get after this 20 minute full body AMRAP 💪🔥
.
You don’t actually need a partner for this one. You can totally crush it solo, BUT I encourage you all to find a workout buddy because you are 2X more likely to stick to your fitness regimen with a one! 👯‍♀️
.
You’re also more likely to work harder, push out that last rep, run a little faster, go the extra mile, or hang in there for another minute. When you do, you’ll see better & faster results! It’s a win win! All those kudos, “well dones”, high-fives or pats on the back matter. Having a training partner can be an added boost to help you keep going & reach new heights. 🙌
.
Did you know that I have a Power Partner Training Guide?! The PPG is perfect for anyone who wants to get better with a buddy! It doesn’t matter if it’s your significant other, your best friend, your co-worker, your mom, your brother or someone else. Find that someone who can hold you accountable & push you to your limits!
.
WORKOUT DEETS 👇
.
PART 1 - Begin with 3x10 reps of heavy back squats (clip shown last). Rest 2 minutes & add more weight between each set.
.
Once finished, rest 5 mins & get set up for part 2.
.
PART 2 - For 20 minutes, complete as many rounds as possible of the following circuit. Rest as needed, as minimally as possible.
.
1️⃣ WALL BALLS
OR burpees
💥 40 reps
.
2️⃣ DB ALT. POWER SNATCHES
OR DB renegade rows + push up
💥 10 reps
.
3️⃣ TOES TO BAR
OR V-Ups
💥 20 reps
.
4️⃣ ROW
OR run
💥 24 calories OR run 300 meters
.
Tag your workout partner & crime & get after this one. 💪
.
Mine was my strong, beautiful, talented, rad, kind friend @yogoskenz . Can I also take a moment to appreciate how bomb she looks in my CPT sunny mustard leggings?! 😍🔥💛
.
.
.
#teamcpt #fullbodyworkout #amrap #wodoftheday #workoutmotivation #partnerworkout #workoutpartner #personaltrainer #iamstphorm #mauihawaii

node.text:
My kind of home gym. 🚐💪
.
If you travel often, if you don’t always have access to a equipment, or if you just don’t have the time or desire to go to the gym all the time, I know you’ll love & benefit from my Home Body training Guides. These aren’t only the programs That I personally followed over the past year, but almost 100,000 others have downloaded them since 2020!! 😱 They are challenging whether you are a beginner or an elite athlete! Luckily, you always carry your best piece of equipment...YOU! 🤗
.
Learn more information & see all the training programs I offer at clairepthomas.com (link in bio). 
.
ALSO, If you have a van & you’re interested in a pull-up bar like mine, this exact bar is actually available to the public! 💪 My friends at @adventurevancamp & I designed this custom for my van. It turned out so awesome & so many people have been interested that we decided we should make more. 🤗 Head to their website for all the deets!
.
Have a great day you guys. I’m so grateful you’re here. Reach out if there’s anything you need. 💛
.
.
#teamcpt #vanlife #vanlifediaries #vanlifemovement #sprintervanconversion #sprintervan #outdoorworkout #personaltrainer #mauihawaii #pullups #abworkout #strongwomen #iamstphorm

Start your week off on the right foot (& the left), with this spicy leg workout! 🔥
.
Hey guys! Hope you had an amazing weekend. We sure did! We cruised around parts of the island we had never seen, found seaglass, made new friends, reunited with old friends, ate delicious food, threw some fire, jumped from some cliffs, drank some wine & made many memories we’ll never forget. ☺️
.
Now, it’s time to get back to work & back on track towards my goals.
.
Today is the LAST DAY to get signed up for the FREE $50,000 8 week Summer Challenge! 💪 
.
If you’ve been waiting for the right time to get back in shape & to take control of your life again, this is your chance!
.
I want to coach you & welcome you to join my AMAZING Team!
.
I can’t convince you to start, though. It’s all up to you.
.
When you download the free app, you’ll have access to a FREE personalized meal plan & FREE home & gym training plans. You can measure your success w/ the progress photo & weight-in tracker.
.
The best part of all is that you’ll have the incredible support of my online Facebook fitness community, TeamCPT. This is where I have exclusive live workouts, Q&A’s, discounts, recipes, AMAZING giveaways, prizes, & more! 🙌
.
✨Download the app & join my Team with the links in my bio! ✨
.
So much more info is in my Facebook group, so head there for all the deets & shoot me a DM if you have any questions. 🤗
.
OKAY, now for the workout deets 👇
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ LEG EXTENSIONS
💥 12 reps
2️⃣ LEG CURLS
💥 12 reps
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ KB CURTSY LUNGES
💥 8 reps each way
2️⃣ LATERAL LUNGES
💥 8 reps each way
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ SLED PUSHES
💥 50-60 meters
2️⃣ WALKING PULSE LUNGE + KICK UP
💥 10 reps each way
.
Good luck, you’re gonna need it. 😅
.
Save for your next leg day & tag your workout homies who needs to get after this one. 👊
.
#teamcpt #mondaymotivation #personaltrainer #legdayworkout #iam1stphorm #legworkout #legday #workoutoftheday

node.text:
The secret to getting ahead is getting started. Today is the perfect day for new beginnings. ✨
.
I love Sunday’s because it’s not only the day that I reflect on the goods & the bads from my previous week, but it’s also the day that I set myself up for an even better week ahead.
.
Ask yourself if what you’re doing today is getting you closer to where you want to be tomorrow.
.
If it’s not, you can change that. It comes down to one simple decision.
.
Everything that happens in your life begins with a decision. Tony Robins said that in your moments of decision, your destiny is shaped.
.
If you don’t make decisions today about how you’re going to live, then you’ve already made your decision to let your environment shape your destiny. 
.
Determine not just what you’d like to become. Decide who you are COMMITTED to being.
.
Commit NOW because tomorrow is the last day to join me for the FREE life changing $50,000 Summer Challenge!! 🙌
.
I would absolutely love to coach you, get to know you & get better beside you over the next 8 weeks!
.
Download the free app with the link in my bio & learn more through my “challenge” highlight & my previous posts. DM me if you have any questions at all. 😊
.
Can’t wait to welcome more of you to my amazing #teamcpt ! 💛💪

node.text:
Crazy core workout challenge + GIVEAWAY! 👊🔥
.
Happy Saturday guys! ☺️
.
Starting now, I’ll be sharing a weekly core challenge & one lucky person who tries it will receive a free CPT Fit Guide of choice!
.
All you have to do is film yourself or a friend ATTEMPTING (it doesn’t have to look pretty 😆) an exercise from this workout, tag me on your story & use the hashtag, #clairecorechallenge 💪
.
I’m NOT choosing the winners based on how well or how many reps. The weekly winner will be selected completely randomly from the pool of people who tag me throughout each week! 🙌
.
So, grab a set of heavy kettle bells & give this workout a shot! Tag your homies who also need to try for a chance to win one of my training programs. 💪
.
To learn more about all the programs I offer, click the link in my bio for my website!
.
I will announce the winner on my story next weekend, when I share next week’s new core challenge!
.
GOOD LUCK! 😅
.
.
.

node.text:
Getting & staying in shape is HARD & I’m not talking physically.
.
The biggest challenge isn’t the ache in your lungs or the burning in your legs. It’s that little voice in your head telling you, “I can’t.”
.
After spending most of my life as a competitive athlete, I taught myself how to drown out those doubts & to push harder in those difficult moments of weakness.
.
There’s one thought that my mind always returns to when I’m on the verge of giving up. All I have to do it remind myself WHY I started on this journey.
.
My “why” is you.
.
My mission is to help that little voice in your head fade away too. For you to whisper to yourself when you are in pain & about to quit, “Actually, I can.”
.
Your potential is limitless, but you have to start first. This is me nudging you to take those first steps towards a healthier you. Trust me, it’s worth it & I believe in you. I’ll be here to support & help you every step of the way.
.
👉You have a few ways left to sign up for the FREE $50,000 8 week Summer Challenge!
.
If you’ve been waiting for the right time to get back in shape & to take control of your life again, this is your chance!
.
I want to coach you & welcome you to join my AMAZING Team!
.
I can’t convince you to start, though. It’s all up to you.
.
When you download the free app, you’ll have access to a FREE personalized meal plan & FREE home & gym training plans. You can measure your success w/ the progress photo & weight-in tracker.
.
The best part of all is that you’ll have the incredible support of my online Facebook fitness community, TeamCPT. This is where I have exclusive live workouts, Q&A’s, discounts, recipes, AMAZING giveaways, prizes, & more! 🙌
.
✨Download the app & join my Team with the links in my bio! ✨
.
So much more info is in my Facebook group, so head there for all the deets & shoot me a DM if you have any questions. 🤗
.
The official start date is July 12th, but you can get started right NOW! What are you waiting for? It’s FREE!
.
No more excuses. No more putting it off for another time. No more complaining. This is YOUR life & YOUR health. Take control of it & join me for the next 8 weeks. 💛
.
#teamcpt #fitnesschallenge #personaltrainer

Back & triceps straight outta my CPT Fit Guide 2.0! 💪🔥
.
If you enjoy supersets, you’ll love my CPT Fit Guide 2.0! For those of you who don’t know, a superset is when you alternate between two exercises for one combined set, with minimal rest in between. You can rest after all reps of both exercises are completed. Personally, I prefer supersets because they make my workouts go by faster & they are more fun. 🤗
.
I’m currently alternating between bodybuilding style workouts like this one, CrossFit & my outdoor bodyweight workouts.
.
If you’re interested in following a training program for any or all of these training styles, I’ve got you covered! Check out the Fit Guides I offer & personally use myself at clairepthomas.com or click the link in my bio. 💪
.
Swipe to the very end & screenshot the workouts deets & to get a feel for what my fit guide looks like.
.
My favorite part about my digital training programs is that each exercise is linked to a video tutorial. So, you can click on the title of each exercise & a video of me will pop up, demonstrating proper form & technique if you are unsure. 🙌
.
Please reach out if you ever have any questions about my Guides & learn more info on my website.
.
Tag your workout homie & save this one for later! 👊
.
.
.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Claire P. Thomas on July 08, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
High intensity cardio & core crusher!💪🏃🏼‍♀️
.
Save this one for the next time you’re short on time & due for a soul sucking sweat sesh! 🔥
.
You can also pick a different piece of cardio equipment (assault bike, bike, treadmill, ski erg...) & do the same format! 🙌
.
D E E T S :
.
Set a 25 minute timer & complete the following 3 exercises every 5 minutes for 5 rounds. The goal is to complete each exercise as quickly as possible, so that you can rest the remainder of the 5 minutes.
.
Every 5 minutes for 5 total rounds:
.
1️⃣ ROW
🔥 12 calories
2️⃣ TOES TO BAR (or hanging knee raises)
🔥 12 reps
3️⃣ RUN
🔥 300 meters
.
Your turn. 👊
.
Have you signed up for the FREE 8 week Summer Challenge yet?! You still have some time! Check out my previous post & “Challenge” highlight for more deets and sign up with the link in my bio! I’d be honored to welcome you to my amazing team! 💛
.
Tag your HIIT lovin workout buddies & get after it!💪
.
.
.
#teamcpt #hiit #fullbodyworkout  #hiitworkout #workoutmotivation #personaltrainer #cardioworkout #coreworkout #fitnesscoach #iam1stphorm #legionofboom
